    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This driver-spec example features a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and has received essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains precise with upgraded poly-bushings, while the limited-slip differential ensures linear power delivery through the rear wheels. Though it exhibits minor cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the compression across all six cylinders is within factory spec, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator for improved thermal management. A tactile, performance-oriented machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
